Suppose for a phone number , we need only particular length
Put the following line in your XML of EDIT Text

android:maxLength="10"

So that it looks like

 <EditText
                android:id="@+id/phone"
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:inputType="phone"  <!-- OR "number" -->
                android:maxLength="10"
                android:textSize="17sp"
                tools:ignore="TextFields" />
